{"tid":1314324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我想見的達哥 只有懷念，不懂 怎去做兄弟","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:26:25.000Z","uid":36497,"like":44,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0faab44b1d210a5a8501e9005c90b7bcfaa8a053","tid":1314324,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"拍廣告 無可避免 達哥總依戀金錢<br />\nSLEEPING DOG  忍耐著呵欠 完全為兄弟快樂~<br />\n<br />\n尋得到 完美世界 回不到初心那天<br />\n靈氣大概早被污染 誰為了生活不變<br />\n<br />\n越渴望見面然後發現<br />\n中間隔著那十年<br />\n我想見的達哥 只有懷念<br />\n不懂 怎去做兄弟<br />\n<br />\n像我在往日還未反面<br />\n林慧韡怎麼變遷<br />\n似等了一百年 忽爾明白<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPav%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=26ed0ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n即使再開台 成熟地表演 不如不見"},{"pid":"a61c3242ca9e96ff18806b90cfa2f9c1f5f3b708","tid":1314324,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"未load到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb7b55e7097cbaa3d29e7549d52b9e0f29cb74c","tid":1314324,"uid":90174,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"樓主係魔鏡歌詞網打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29958418845946a89458fa56dd996f236fa4c6e","tid":1314324,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"古巨基？"},{"pid":"ebe54f286693ad18c37517f1501c64ff0b9a7f01","tid":1314324,"uid":191815,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPav%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=26ed0ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1703